Signed-off-by: Angelo Ribeiro <angelo.ribeiro@synopsys.com>
Tested-by: Yannick Fertre <yannick.fertre@st.com>
Tested-by: Adrian Pop <pop.adrian61@gmail.com>
Acked-by: Neil Armstrong <narmstrong@baylibre.com>
